					07 3 Track Write MCRW																																		  
					08 Track 2 Smart Card Reader/Writer																											  
					09 Track 3 Smart Card Reader																															
					0A 3 Track Write Smart Card Reader																												
					0B Dip Card Reader (track 1/2 and track 2/3)																							
					0C Track 1/2/3 with CIM86																																  
					11 Swipe Card Reader																																			
